&ldquo;We will be doing another crossover event this fall on The CW [and] we will be introducing a new character. We will be fighting alongside Batwoman,&rdquo; Arrow star Stephen Amell shared on Thursday at the network&rsquo;s Upfronts event.<br />
<br />
In turn, as one might surmise, &ldquo;We&rsquo;re adding the city of Gotham into the Arrowverse,&rdquo; added CW president Mark Pedowitz, promising &ldquo;another full-throttled action packed event.&rdquo;
